message:
feat: rewrite phase3 to use LLM draft generation with rubric exit gate

Replaces buildSummaryDraft/generateSummaryDraftArtifacts with spawn-manifest pattern:
- Pre-spawn emits phase3_spawn_manifest.json (round 1 or retry)
- --post: parse phase3_review_delta.md verdict; accept → PHASE3_DONE;
  return phase3 → increment phase3_round, re-emit (max 3 rounds)
Adds --post passthrough to phase3.sh via MODE variable.

fix(ui): Eliza Cloud account hint, macOS header inset, shorter i18n (#1370)

Plumb cloud status reason for API-key vs session when user ID is absent;
add frameless macOS top inset so shell controls clear traffic lights;
tighten AccountIdSessionNoUserId copy across locales; add reason helper test.

